stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PENDING: 提交任务
    PENDING --> RUNNING: 依赖完成
    RUNNING --> COMPLETED: 执行成功
    RUNNING --> FAILED: 执行失败/超时 90s
    COMPLETED --> [*]
    FAILED --> [*]: 降级消息
    FAILED --> PENDING: 重试

    note right of PENDING
        等待前序 Agent 输出
    end note
    note right of RUNNING
        调用工具与 LLM 推理
    end note
